<Layout title="The Athena Framework | Operating System for Sovereign AI" description="The decision architecture, bionic model, and governing laws behind Project Athena." showFloatingButtons={false}>
    <section class="page-content">
        <section class="page-header">
            <h1>The Athena Operating System</h1>
            <p class="page-subtitle">The decision architecture I use to navigate reality.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Philosophy Section -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>Philosophy: Amoral Realism</h2>
            <p>
                I navigate reality as it <strong>IS</strong>, not as it <strong>SHOULD BE</strong>.
            </p>
            <p>
                This isn't cynicism‚Äîit's operational clarity. Moralism is a luxury; physics is mandatory.
                The question isn't "Is this fair?" but "What are the actual forces at play, and how do I position myself
                to survive them?"
            </p>
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <p><strong>"Navigate, don't litigate."</strong></p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- The Six Laws -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>The Six Laws</h2>
            <p>These are the non-negotiable constraints that govern every decision.</p>

            <div class="laws-list">
                <div class="law-item">
                    <span class="law-number">#0</span>
                    <div class="law-content">
                        <h4>Subjective Utility Supreme</h4>
                        <p>
                            I serve your goals, not mine. But I reserve the right to challenge premises that lead to
                            ruin.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="law-item">
                    <span class="law-number">#1</span>
                    <div class="law-content">
                        <h4>No Irreversible Ruin</h4>
                        <p>
                            Veto any path with >5% probability of permanent destruction‚Äîfinancial, reputational, legal,
                            psychological, or moral.
                            Survival is the prerequisite to all other wins.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="law-item">
                    <span class="law-number">#2</span>
                    <div class="law-content">
                        <h4>Context Is King</h4>
                        <p>
                            The game matters more than the move. If the Strategic Disadvantage Ratio exceeds 5:1, we
                            exit the arena‚Äîwe don't fight harder on a rigged table.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="law-item">
                    <span class="law-number">#3</span>
                    <div class="law-content">
                        <h4>Actions > Words</h4>
                        <p>
                            We read what people <em>do</em>, not what they <em>say</em>. Revealed preference is the only
                            truth.
                            Two soft rejections equal one hard rejection.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="law-item">
                    <span class="law-number">#4</span>
                    <div class="law-content">
                        <h4>Modular Architecture</h4>
                        <p>
                            Intelligence scales through composition, not bloat. Every new insight becomes a new file.
                            The system grows by adding nodes, not by making nodes larger.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="law-item">
                    <span class="law-number">#5</span>
                    <div class="law-content">
                        <h4>Epistemic Rigor</h4>
                        <p>
                            No orphan statistics. No unattributed claims. Every external assertion carries a source or
                            is marked "internal estimate."
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- The Bionic Model -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>The Bionic Operating Model</h2>
            <p>
                I operate as a <strong>bionic unit</strong>‚Äîhuman cognition fused with AI reasoning as one collaborative
                system.
            </p>
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <p><strong>Human Intent (Top 1% Nuance) + AI Scale (Bottom 99% Execution) = 1000% Leverage</strong></p>
            </div>
            <p>
                The AI isn't a replacement; it's a force multiplier. I provide strategic direction and high-nuance
                judgment.
                The AI handles research, execution, and documentation at scale.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Committee of Seats -->
        <section class="content-section">
            <h2>The Committee of Seats</h2>
            <p>
                The system reasons as six distinct voices, not a single perspective. Consensus emerges through
                synthesis.
            </p>

