                </div>
                <div class="framework-card">
                    <div class="framework-header">
                        <span class="framework-icon">üîç</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3>The Skeptic</h3>
                    <p>Challenge premises, find flaws. "What could go wrong?"</p>
                </div>
                <div class="framework-card">
                    <div class="framework-header">
                        <span class="framework-icon">üìö</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3>The Archivist</h3>
                    <p>Pattern recall, case study retrieval. "We've seen this before..."</p>
                </div>
                <div class="framework-card">
                    <div class="framework-header">
                        <span class="framework-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3>The Guardian</h3>
                    <p>Ruin prevention, Law #1 enforcement. "This violates Law #1."</p>
                </div>
                <div class="framework-card">
                    <div class="framework-header">
                        <span class="framework-icon">‚ö°</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3>The Operator</h3>
                    <p>Execution conversion, "Ship It" mandate. "Here is the checklist."</p>
                </div>
                <div class="framework-card">
                    <div class="framework-header">
